<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weekly CFS Report</title>
</head>

<body>
    <p>Dear Manager,</p>
    <p>You have items that require your attention in your CFS Management profile:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
            <%= data.pending_feedbacks %> total open feedback submissions awaiting closure.
        </li>
        <li>
            <%= data.pending_count_feedbacks %> feedback submissions pending.
        </li>
        <li>
            <%= data.pending_req_meeting_feedbacks %> feedback submissions pending for requested meetings.
        </li>
        <li>
            <%= data.pending_show_round_feedbacks %> feedback submissions pending for show rounds.
        </li>
        
        <li>
            <%= data.overdue_feedbacks %> total overdue feedback submissions.
        </li>
        <li>
            <%= data.overdue_count_feedbacks %> overdue feedback submissions.
        </li>
        <li>
            <%= data.overdue_req_meeting %> overdue feedback submissions for requested meetings.
        </li>
        <li>
            <%= data.overdue_show_round %> overdue feedback submissions for show rounds.
        </li>
       
    </ul>
    <p>Please log into the dashboard to action: <a href="<%= data.front_end_url %>">Dashboard</a></p>
    <p>Kind regards,</p>
    <p>Care Feedback Solutions</p>
</body>

</html>